OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBecoming quite windy as cloud
OL,6,Fand rain spread east through the
OL,7,Fmorning, heavy at times. Brighter
OL,8,Fspells developing from the west
OL,9,Fthrough late afternoon as the rain
OL,10,Fclears east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLargely dry with clear spells
OL,13,Fthrough the evening and overnight, but
OL,14,Fthe odd shower feeding in from the
OL,15,Fwest. Occasionally blustery southwest
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
