OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FLargely dry morning with
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells, though with
OL,7,Fthe chance of the odd shower. Cloudier
OL,8,Fin the afternoon with some evening
OL,9,Frain. A bit cooler than recent days.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,12,FSaturday morning with some outbreaks
OL,13,Fof rain, becoming drier and brighter
OL,14,Flater. Cloudy and windy at times with
OL,15,Foccasional spells of rain on Sunday
OL,16,Fand Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
